@startuml pipeline
title GamefyDB ETL Pipeline

skinparam defaultFontName Monospaced
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #EEF4FF
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #5566AA

|Source|
start
:4 × .xls files\n(cash, sessions, stock, members);

|ingestor.py|
:_read_raw()\nxlrd.open_workbook → DataFrame\n(no header, all strings);
:_strip_artifacts()\nDrop title/date/blank/page-break/\nheader/footer rows;\n
note right
  COLUMN_MAPS holds\n  empirically verified\n  xlrd column indices
end note
:ingest_all() → dict[str, DataFrame]\nraw string DataFrames;

|cleaner.py|
:per-file clean functions\n_clean_cash / _clean_sessions\n_clean_stock / _clean_members;
note right
  parse_amount()   → float (strips \\u202f)\n  parse_datetime() → datetime\n  parse_duration() → int (minutes)\n  extract_terminal() → name from (COMMENT)
end note
:clean_all() → dict[str, DataFrame]\ntyped + normalised;

|transformer.py|
:build_dims()\nUnion natural keys → surrogate IDs\n4 dimension tables;
:build_facts()\n_resolve_fk() maps natural → surrogate\n4 fact tables;
:transform() → dict[str, DataFrame]\n4 dims + 4 facts;

|writer.py|
if (--format?) then (csv)
  :write CSVs\ndims/  →  dim_*.csv\nfacts/ →  fact_*.csv;
else (excel)
  :write gamefydb.xlsx\none sheet per table;
endif

|Output|
:Star-schema dataset\nready for DWH import;
stop

@enduml
